data.title: Amber Rose Reacts to Ex Wiz Khalifa and Aimee Aguilar's Pregnancy News
data.meta_description: Wiz Khalifa celebrated Father's Day by revealing he and girlfriend Aimee Aguilar are expecting a baby. The "Black and Yellow" artist is already dad to son Sebastian, whom he shares with ex Amber Rose.
data.text:
Roll up and congratulate Wiz Khalifa.

The "Young, Wild & Free" artist revealed on Father's Day that he's expecting a young one with girlfriend Aimee Aguilar.

In a June 16 Instagram announcement, Khalifa could be seen resting his hand on Aguilar's growing baby bump as she held up a pregnancy testâ€”with the rapper writing, "Baby Girl On The Way."

And several stars congratulated the couple on the big news, including his ex Amber Rose.

"We can't wait to meet her!" the model, with whom Khalifa shares 11-year-old son Sebastian, commented. Added the musician's "See You Again" collaborator Charlie Puth, "Congratulations Wiz!!!!!!!"

Aguilar, 30, also celebrated by posting pictures from her maternity photoshoot. Plus, she and Khalifa, 36, gave fans a glimpse inside what appeared to be her baby shower.
